item.description:
This day is open to all climbers, but let me know ASAP if you need gear so I can bring it for you. Do not go to the part of the State park where the big lake is. The climbing is located from Reservation rd, in Deerfield. Please check w/ me for exact directions if you don't know how to get there or we can meet before driving into the park. It can get confusing and I don't want people to miss out becasue they are lost :)
I will be parking down at round pond, end of the road basically. There is a place to swim after too so bring a suit as it may be HOT out that day.
Hope to see you all then
Kellie
item.how_to_find_us: Look for the green van and meetup signs
item.name: Pawtuckaway Day
